Sort__c.label: Sort#
Sort__c.description: This field is used to determine the display sequence of the charges on the quote

Context__c.label: Context
Context__c.description:
POPS-6057
It can be one of the values: CsAgent, InAppPopUp, CancellationFlow, CRM

RenewalConsentGivenDate__c.label: RenewalConsentGivenDate
RenewalConsentGivenDate__c.description: The last date on which a user has given consent for his subscription to be renewed. Currently needed for a regulation in Quebec where a user has to give consent for his yearly subscription to renew.

RiskProfile__c.label: Risk Profile
RiskProfile__c.description: Field used to capture current risk of subscription churning. This can be used in conjunction when tracking non billable usage.

Action_Perform__c.label: Action_Perform
Action_Perform__c.description: Custom field that synchronizes to Salesforce and helps in identification which email to customer should be triggered. Possible values: Set Pause, Edit Pause, Edit resume dates in pause, Cancel scheduled pause, Early resume, Cancel subscription, Cancel subscription in pause, Resume from pause.

RoadmapPriority__c.label: Roadmap Priority
RoadmapPriority__c.description: Custom field used to support reporting and analysis.

PostSignUpGiftcode__c.label: PostSignUpGiftcode
PostSignUpGiftcode__c.description: Giftode number (Giftcode redeemed post sign up)

PostSignUpGiftcodeCampaignName__c.label: PostSignUpGiftcodeCampaignName
PostSignUpGiftcodeCampaignName__c.description: Campaign Name for a giftcode used post sign up & stored in the other field:"PostSignUpGiftcode"

discountpercentage__c.label: discountpercentage
discountpercentage__c.description: discount percentage for PPV bundle rate plan

entitlementsetid__c.label: entitlementsetid
entitlementsetid__c.description: The field to present an entitlement to the purchased fixture.

PPVtype__c.label: PPVtype
PPVtype__c.description: The field needed to differentiate PPV rate plans used on sign up and post sign up.

LeadCreditStatus__c.label: Lead Credit Status
LeadCreditStatus__c.description: This field indicates if lead credits are active for the customer i.e. if customer doesn't pay his invoice then as 1st step of collection his lead credits will be paused and tradie will not be able accept jobs

PaymentCommitmentDate__c.label: Payment Commitment Date
PaymentCommitmentDate__c.description: Date that customer has committed to paying their account. Collections Agents should not have to reach out until then if payment still hasn't been made after this date.

AutomatedDowngradeDate__c.label: Automated Downgrade Date
AutomatedDowngradeDate__c.description: Used as part of automated downgraded processes

CreditHold__c.label: Credit Hold
CreditHold__c.description: Date the Customer was last placed on Credit Hold
